      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>This update to the Employment Tribunal confirms that we have now published the government response to the consultation on proposals for amendments to the Fee-Paid Judicial Pension Scheme in order to provide a substantive remedy for O’Brien 2 and Miller claimants.</p>
</div>

</div>
